Description: Sherd of rim and wall of local Egyptian pottery dinos; orange micaceous clay; once polished surface with horizontal burnishing; incised inscription on outside just below rim.
Bibliographic references: Schlotzhauer & Villing 2006 / East Greek Pottery from Naukratis: The Current State of Research (p.55 Table 1, p. 63 fig. 34)
Schlotzhauer 2012 / Untersuchungen zur archaischen griechischen Keramik aus Naukratis (p. 174, NAU 144, pl. 31g-l)
Villing et al 2013-2015 / Naukratis: Greeks in Egypt (IA.04)
